---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroImg from '../components/HeroImg.astro';
import heroImg from '../images/index/wph-hero.webp';
---

<Layout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | Wedding Photo Hangover</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta name="description" content="Oops! This page doesn’t exist. Maybe try going back to the homepage or exploring our podcast and blog content." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="404 - Page Not Found | Wedding Photo Hangover" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Oops! This page doesn’t exist. Maybe try going back to the homepage or exploring our podcast and blog content." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://weddinghangover.com/404" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/images/global/WPH_Wide_CleanNB.webp" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="404 - Page Not Found | Wedding Photo Hangover" />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Oops! This page doesn’t exist. Maybe try going back to the homepage or exploring our podcast and blog content." />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="/images/global/WPH_Wide_CleanNB.webp" />
  </Fragment>
  <HeroImg 
    title="OH NO!" 
    background={heroImg} 
  />
  <main>
    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="privacy-wrapper">
            <section>
                <h1>404 – Page Not Found</h1>
            </section>
            <section>
                <p>
                    Well this is just outright embarrassing. I don't know if it's more embarrassing for you or more embarrassing for us.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section>
                <p>  
                    You somehow navigated to a non-existent page. If you're certain that we should be embarrassed, then send us an email at <a href="mailto:weddingphotohangover@gmail.com?subject=You%20Should%20Be%20Embarrassed&body=This%20is%20embarrassing%20for%20you,%20please%20fix%20this.">weddingphotohangover@gmail.com</a>
                </p>
            </section>
            <section>
                <p>
                    If you think this is your mistake, and not ours... then hang your head and return to the homepage, like a coward.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section>
                <a href="/">
                    Return to homepage
                </a>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
